item.title: CVE-2022-4788|2024-08-03T01:48:40.473Z -- unknown -- embed%20pdf
item.description: The Embed PDF WordPress plugin through 1.0.6 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
